            "type": "text",
            "text": "RAGAS (Retrieval Augmented Generation Assessment) is an open-source framework for evaluating RAG pipelines without requiring human-labeled test sets for most metrics. It scores four dimensions of RAG quality using LLM-as-judge internally, producing a single composite RAGAS Score from a harmonic mean."
