      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "RAGAS provides a reference-free evaluation suite purpose-built for RAG pipelines:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Faithfulness",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 catches generator hallucinations beyond the retrieved context."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Answer Relevancy",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 detects off-topic or meandering answers using embedding similarity."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Context Precision",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 diagnoses retriever precision; penalizes irrelevant passages ranked high."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Context Recall",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 identifies retrieval gaps; requires a ground-truth reference answer."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Three of the four metrics require no labeled test set, making RAGAS suitable for both offline benchmark evaluation and online production monitoring. The RAGAS Score (harmonic mean of all four) provides a single number that captures the holistic health of the retrieval-generation pipeline."
